dingding IRC bot
----------------

My personal little IRC bot, used to flex my Erlang muscles.

Read http://fossil.gertm.eu/dingding/index (the actual repo) for more info.

Feel free to:
    * Suggest features
    * Report bugs
    * Submit patches
    * Fork
    * Read the code
    * Comment on the code.

